text: Anaconda is an upcoming American action comedy horror movie. It is expected to be released on December 25, 2025. It was directed by Tom Gormican and produced by Brad Fuller and Andrew Form. It is a reboot of the 1997 movie of the same name. It is also the sixth movie in the Anaconda series. The movie follows a group of friends who decide to shoot a remake of their favourite movie in the jungle and come across a massive anaconda.
